title: Chicago XXV (25) -- The Christmas Album
description:
Take a bunch of public-domain songs, put them on a album that will sell a bunch every year and what does that make -- money...

If you ever see Chicago in concert now, they usually whip out "Let It Snow" on tour as their shamless seasonal plug.  Plus they&#039;ve got this really weak snow machine they sometimes whip out.  But the band is good, they&#039;re still rocking.
